TCHK1C                     KFLD           H@KAKE
     C                     KFLD           H@ZAIS
     C                     KFLD           S@ZAIK
     C                     KFLD           K@YM    60
     C           K#BTA     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           S@PRT1
     C                     KFLD           S@PRT2
     C                     KFLD           S@PRT3
     C                     KFLD           K@YM    60
     C           K#MC      KLIST
