     C                     ENDSR
      *------------------------------------------------------
      *   DATE SET
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           #DSET     BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     X       30
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     Z       30
